 center of the village. There is also a limestone quarry from which white limestone is extracted. The village is towered by St\u00edrka Hill, which dominates the general area with its height of 702 m above sea level. Southwest of the village is a natural monument Dolejsi drahy .\n\n== Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nFile:Nehodiv, zat\u00e1\u010dka.jpg|Houses\nFile:Nehodiv6.jpg|House\nFile:Nehodiv5.jpg|Village square with tree\n</gallery>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20080618131004/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0322/ Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Klatovy District]\n\n{{commons category|Nehodiv}}\n{{Klatovy District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villages in Klatovy District]]\n", "name_user": "Jonnychiwa", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200ePopulation", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nehodiv"}
